MemcachedImpl
public class ChurnTolerantDHTImpl<V extends java.io.Serializable>
extends BasicDHTImpl<V>

A churn-tolerant implementation of DHT service. This implementations adds churn tolerance techniques to the basic implementation. Those techniques include replication, join-time transfer, multiple get and repeated implicit put.
